(all measurements are estimates)

filling:
1 lb ground beef
1 small onion
2 cloves garlic
spinach (optional)

1 can tomatoes
1 can tomato sauce
1 can tomato paste
2 Tbsp italian seasoning
1 tsp salt
1/2 tsp garlic powder
black pepper

cheese:
1 egg
1 cup shredded mozzarella
1 cup ricotta
1/2 cup parmesan

Brown the ground beef and cook in the onions and garlic.
Add the spinach, tomatoes, and spices.

Mix all the cheeses with the egg.

Layer in a baking dish with lasagna noodles and cook
as per noodle instructions.  eg 40 minutes @ 350Â°F
